:: Battera::

She gave a small himt of a smile.  She wanted to go back home as much 
as Vulois did.  She looked at him, "Ah,  We need to find a safe place 
to stay while we do this.  Uh, we can use the cave. So far as I know, 
we are the only ones that know about this cave."  She thought about 
the cord in her shoulder.  It would serve as a link connection, but 
she hoped her programs would be able to stand up to Vulois.  If his 
anti-tamper programs were too strong, she wouldn't be able to get 
in.  She looked at Cybershark and smiled,"Well, I guess then you get 
first watch huh?" she tilted her head slighty and gave him  a warm 
smile. She took a step forward and kissed his cheek." Thank you."
She then walked into the cave. She smiled and looked around,"You 
know, a few curtains, a little paint, a few more windows, and this 
place would be down right cozzy." she said with a chuckle.
